  "id" : "api/http/XHRConnection",
  "title" : "XHRConnection",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"xhrconnection\">XHRConnection</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label deprecated\">deprecated</label>\n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/http\">@angular/http</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/http/XHRConnection\" class=\"code-anchor\">XHRConnection</a> } from <a href=\"api/http\">'@angular/http'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/http/src/backends/xhr_backend.ts#L23-L180\">http/src/backends/xhr_backend.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"deprecated\">\n  <h2 id=\"deprecation-notes\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dxhln38nrp36303qqb6hgjwp9\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>弃用说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"76x00miep182jnm2o7zo0lf26\">改用 @angular/common/http</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ivgu86loww6mg4fq1brezlnd\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/http/XHRConnection\" class=\"code-anchor\">XHRConnection</a> implements <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/http/Connection\">Connection</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/http/XHRConnection#constructor()\">constructor(req: Request, browserXHR: BrowserXhr, baseResponseOptions?: ResponseOptions)</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/http/XHRConnection#request\">request: Request</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/http/XHRConnection#response\">response: Observable&lt;Response&gt;</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/http/XHRConnection#readyState\">readyState: ReadyState</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/http/XHRConnection#setDetectedContentType\">setDetectedContentType(req: any, _xhr: any)</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ebumzes0jfxvkk3fzuyaryed9\">使用 \n<code>XMLHttpRequest</code> 创建连接。给定一个完全限定的请求， \n<code><a href=\"api/http/XHRConnection\" class=\"code-anchor\">XHRConnection</a></code> 将立即创建一个 \n<code>XMLHttpRequest</code> 对象并发送请求。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bsgeu7zymil5pnwub0oj84ycm\">此类通常不会在应用程序内部直接创建或交互，尽管 \n<a href=\"api/http/testing/MockConnection\"><code>MockConnection</code></a> 可以在测试中进行交互。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"constructors\">\n  <h2 id=\"constructor\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"64p310lbzdqiret0qyhhannvq\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>构造函数</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"constructor\">\n  <a id=\"constructor()\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(req: <a href=\"api/http/Request\" class=\"code-anchor\">Request</a>, browserXHR: <a href=\"api/http/BrowserXhr\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserXhr</a>, baseResponseOptions?: <a href=\"api/http/ResponseOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">ResponseOptions</a>)</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"request\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">request: <a href=\"api/http/Request\" class=\"code-anchor\">Request</a></code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"response\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">response: Observable&lt;<a href=\"api/http/Response\" class=\"code-anchor\">Response</a>&gt;</code-example>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"71f0kq4c8e6uqd03yubr3c9nj\">响应 \n<a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\"><code>EventEmitter</code></a>，在 \n<code>XMLHttpRequest</code> 的加载事件上发出单个 \n<a href=\"api/http/Response\"><code>Response</code></a> 值。</p>\n\n  </div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"readyState\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">readyState: <a href=\"api/http/ReadyState\" class=\"code-anchor\">ReadyState</a></code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"setDetectedContentType\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">setDetectedContentType(req: any, _xhr: any)</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/http\n - api/http/Connection\n - api/http/XHRBackend\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/EventEmitter\n - api/http\n - api/http/BrowserXhr\n - api/http/Connection\n - api/http/ReadyState\n - api/http/Request\n - api/http/Response\n - api/http/ResponseOptions\n - api/http/XHRConnection#constructor\n - api/http/XHRConnection#constructor()\n - api/http/XHRConnection#deprecation-notes\n - api/http/XHRConnection#description\n - api/http/XHRConnection#members\n - api/http/XHRConnection#overview\n - api/http/XHRConnection#readyState\n - api/http/XHRConnection#request\n - api/http/XHRConnection#response\n - api/http/XHRConnection#setDetectedContentType\n - api/http/XHRConnection#xhrconnection\n - api/http/testing/MockConnection\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/http/src/backends/xhr_backend.ts#L23-L180\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/http\n-->"
